description:
MIKROTRON - a brand of SVS-Vistek GmbH

The MIKROTRON brand is internationally known in the machine vision market for small, particularly robust High-Speed cameras that are used in industrial and scientific applications as well as in sports, advertising and nature filming.

SVS-Vistek GmbH has exceptional know-how in industrial image processing as an innovative manufacturer of high-quality industrial CCD and CMOS cameras for more than 35 years. 
We develop and produce a wide range of standard cameras as well as cameras with the highest resolutions and highest speeds, above-average image quality and all relevant interfaces in our own clean rooms at our headquarters in Gilching near Munich: Quality Made in Germany! 
With subsidiaries in the USA and Japan as well as a large partner network, we can advise, support and serve customers of many markets worldwide.

description: Created in 2003, the Red Bull Air Race World Championship celebrated its landmark 75th race at the 2017 season opener in Abu Dhabi. The Red Bull Air Race World Championship features the world’s best race pilots in a pure motorsport competition that combines speed, precision and skill. Using the fastest, most agile, lightweight racing planes, pilots hit speeds of 370kmh while enduring forces of up to 10G as they navigate a low-level slalom track marked by 25-meter-high, air-filled pylons. In 2014, the Challenger Cup was conceived to help the next generation of pilots develop the skills needed for potential advancement to the Master Class that vies for the World Championship.

description:
Profoto was founded in Stockholm in 1968 by photographer and engineer Eckhard Heine and photography equipment retailer Conny Dufgran. Their relationship began when Conny sold Eckhard a flash unit that didn't work. Annoyed with the faulty unit, Eckhard went home to invent a new type of flash. He returned a couple of weeks later with a superior unit. A few years after that, Eckhard and Conny exhibited the first Pro-1 generator at the Photokina trade show in Cologne. It was an instant success. Profoto was born. With a bang.

Today, our products are used by the best in the industry. Whether it be on a billboard or in a fashion magazine, there's a good chance that the image you are looking at was created with the help of our lights. But even though we continuously refine and improve our equipment, we stay true to Eckhard's and Conny's ideals.

description:
David Bowie redefined musical genres and the potential of live performance for generations of music lovers. Creating and discarding a variety of personae and restlessly challenging musical boundaries, Bowie released timeless albums including Space Oddity, Hunky Dory, The Rise and Fall of Ziggy Stardust…, Aladdin Sane, Diamond Dogs, Young Americans, Station to Station, "Heroes,” Let's Dance, Heathen, The Next Day and many more. Blackstar, Bowie’s 28th and final studio album, was released on his 69th birthday, January 8, 2016. David Bowie died on January 10, 2016, two days after the release of Blackstar. His body of work, his influence on the worlds of music, art, fashion, film, theatre and beyond, and his legacy of innovation and reinvention will live forever. 2022 kicks off with Bowie at 75, a celebration of his 75th birthday with the Brilliant Adventure box set, the previously unreleased Toy, the 50th anniversary of Ziggy Stardust and a series of special events.

description:
UIC is the worldwide organisation for the promotion of #rail transport at a global level and collaborative development of the #railway system. It brings together some 200 members on all 5 continents, among them rail operators, infrastructure managers, railway service providers, etc. UIC maintains close cooperation links with all actors in the rail transport domain right around the world, including manufacturers, railway associations, public authorities and stakeholders in other domains and sectors whose experiences may be beneficial to rail development. The UIC's main tasks include understanding the business needs of the rail community, developing programmes of innovation to identify solutions to those needs and preparing and publishing a series of documents known as IRS that facilitate the implementation of the innovative solutions.

description:
Hey, my name's Austin and this channel focuses on pinball gameplay videos with and without commentary. If you have questions about any game covered here, feel free to ask in the video's comment section and I'll do my best to help.

I've been playing pinball since 2011 and the oldest videos on this channel date back to 2013 when I acquired my first machines and was still a newbie. As such this channel has become a bit of an archived history of my progression as a pinball player. I also used to do dedicated/edited videos, but these days I mostly focus on simple stream captures/recordings. Low effort content, but hopefully you find it useful regardless.

While this is my only pinball channel, you may also stumble on my presence elsewhere, where I have been a part of other pinball streams (Buffalo Pinball, 2017), assisted in running unique pinball events (Pinball Done Quick, 2015 - 2017), as well as managing my other non-pinball YouTube channels (i.e., Gameplay and Talk).

description:
The official BUGATTI YouTube Channel

Since its foundation in 1909 by Ettore Bugatti, the brand has been at the pinnacle of the automotive industry, creating the world’s most powerful and luxurious automobiles from its home in Molsheim, France. In the 1920s, BUGATTI became known for its racing successes as well as in the 1930s for Jean Bugatti’s elegant touring cars. In 1991, the EB110 premiered and set new benchmarks for sports car performance. 

With the introduction of the VEYRON 16.4 in 2005, BUGATTI created an entirely new segment: the hyper sports car, becoming the first production model to break through 1,000 PS and 400 km/h. In 2016, the CHIRON once again redefined speed and usability, culminating in a 1,600 PS version breaking the 300mph barrier. 

Today, BUGATTI is part of the BUGATTI Rimac Group and well underway with the development of the next-generation of BUGATTI hyper sports cars, true to Ettore’s motto "If comparable, it is no longer BUGATTI."

The W&H Group, a family-run company based in Bürmoos, Austria,  is one of the leading manufacturers of dental transmission instruments  & devices in the world. Established in 1890 by the precision  engineers Weber and Hampel, the company was acquired by the Malata  Family in 1958. Innovative product and service solutions, a strong focus  on research and development, vision and social responsibility have made  W&H a successful local and global player. 
The current range  of products includes rotating instruments for restoration and  prosthetics, endodontics, implantology (putting in tooth implants) and  prophylaxis, as well as instruments for the field of hygiene and  maintenance and for dental laboratories. W&H products are among the  best quality instruments on the market and are used in dentists’  practices, dental hospitals, dental laboratories and in micro-surgery.

description:
Iron Maiden are an institution. Over 50 years they’ve come to embody a spirit of fearless creative independence, spectacular live shows, ferocious dedication to their fans, and a cheerful indifference to their critics that’s won them a colossal worldwide following.

Their epic discography includes the studio albums ‘Iron Maiden, ‘Killers’, ‘The Number Of The Beast’, ‘Piece Of Mind’, ‘Powerslave, ‘Somewhere In Time’, and ‘Seventh Son Of A Seventh Son’ right up to their 17th outing – ‘Senjutsu.’
That celebrated catalogue has inspired many classic such as ‘The Trooper’, ‘Wasted Years’, ‘Hallowed Be Thy Name’, ‘The Number Of The Beast’, ‘Wasting Love’, ‘Run To The Hills’, ‘Aces High’, ‘Rime Of The Ancient Mariner’ and ‘2 Minutes to Midnight’. 2024 sees the conclusion of their The Future Past world tour ahead of their newly announced Run For Your Lives tour in 2025/26, celebrating the group’s 50th anniversary. It will include some of the largest venues the band has ever played.

description:
Research at the High Pressure Combustion Laboratory (HPCL), located at the University Park campus of the Pennsylvania State University, has been concentrated in the area of combustion of gaseous, solid, liquid, and gelled propellants for rocket and gun propulsion systems, solid fuels for ramjets and hybrid propulsion systems, and metal combustion. Recently, the scope has been expanded further to cover combustion of airbag propellants, flammability/explosion limit determination of gaseous reactants for commercial applications, and study ablation/erosion of rocket nozzle, internal insulation, and heat-shield materials.

More information can be found at http://www.hpcl.psu.edu/

description:
I play virtual pinball on PC, usually in portrait (vertical) with an original dual shock Playstation controller I'm comfortable with. Keybinded via JoyToKey and x360ce emulating the analog sticks, I find it an enjoyable experience.

You may notice in The Pinball Arcade videos that I may nudge multiple times without tilting or getting tilt warnings, that's because the analog sticks give you a varied [in strength] nudge depending on how hard you flick the stick.

Recent developments in late 2015, someone has made an 'XOutputPlugin' for FreePIE (Free Programmable Input Emulator) so you can send a XInput signal to the game with just a hotkey without the use of x360ce! I've made a thread pertaining to this subject here 
http://pinballarcadefans.com/showthread.php/10816-Are-emulated-inputs-the-answer-for-parity-with-controller-users

description:
Professional Photographer | Tutorials | Technique | Travel | Guides

I am Jason Row, a 35 year plus professional travel photographer and photography educator. Through my website, Udemy and here on Youtube, I will be your photographic mentor, leading you through the deeper mysteries of the art of photography.
But who am I? At 16, with an old Soviet Zenit I won my first competition, three months after taking my first photo. From that moment, I never looked back. I spend 15 years managing photography concessions on cruise ships, traveling the world and building a huge library of travel stock images.
In 2011 I left the ships and with my wife, settled in the beautiful city of Odesa, Ukraine, a base from where I continued to shoot, stock photos and video, around the world.
Due to the invasion of Ukraine, my wife and I have relocated to the beautiful North East of England.

As an Amazon Associate, I earn from qualifying purchases

I got into some PC games such as PREY and FEAR until i found an addiction to WOW.

Eventually I took a break from PC games and went back to console.

After many hours of watching i decided to get a brand new PC and dive in myself and share my gameplay with the world.

I hope you enjoy.

All topics for review are selected by an editorial committee comprised of the most distinguished scholars of the discipline. Annual Reviews articles are written by leading scholars to help researchers and students navigate the vast amount of primary research literature that is available to them. description:
Released by UMe on September 2, 2022, The Sick, The Dying... And The Dead! further establishes MEGADETH as a band that has both defined and repeatedly redefined heavy metal since its formation. The album follows up 2016’s Grammy®-winning Dystopia, which debuted at #3 on the Billboard Top 200 (MEGADETH’s highest chart position since its 1992 classic Countdown to Extinction).

MEGADETH has crafted a record with a visceral energy, heaviness, and sometimes paranormal pace that few would expect from such a seasoned band with so little to prove. The Sick, The Dying... And The Dead! melds the ultra-frenetic riffing, fiercely intricate guitar solos, and adventurous spirit of the quartet’s groundbreaking early output with the musicality and melodicism of its ‘90s songwriting, all laced with signature virtuosity and precision – plus, of course, Mustaine’s singular vocal snarl and wry, take-no-shit lyrical vitriol.

MEGADETH recently wrapped up the European leg of their 2023 Crush The World Tour. The thrash metal pioneers will soon be taking their iconic music to stages across the United States as they continue to cement the latest electrifying chapter in a career that has constantly challenged and surprised. Their journey remains one of resilience, artistic integrity, and unbridled passion, leaving an indelible mark on the world of metal.

“I don’t think we’re nearing the end, not even close,” Dave Mustaine concludes.

description:
Die neuesten Videos auf diesem Kanal sind den Menschen in der Ukraine gewidmet, die vielfach unter Gefahr für ihr Leben die russischen Angriffe abwehren um sich für den Erhalt einer freiheitlich-demokratischen Grundordnung, Pressefreiheit und Rechtsstaatlichkeit in ihrem Land zu engagieren. 

Fernverkehrszüge (ICE Zug und IC Zug), Nahverkehrszüge sowie Zugtechnik bilden den Schwerpunkt auf diesem Kanal. Zu sehen sind vor allem ICE 1, ICE 2, ICE 3, ICE T, Intercity modernisiert, IC 2 Doppelstock und einzelne alte oder besondere Züge. Neben Hochgeschwindigkeitszügen filme ich auch Nahverkehr, Güterzüge, Abfahrtsignale und technische Details wie zum Beispiel die Türen der Züge.


The latest videos on this channel are dedicated to the people in Ukraine, many of whom are fending off Russian attacks at the risk of their lives in order to preserve a free-democratic order, freedom of the press and the rule of law in their country.

If you want to use any footage for a review or anything like that then just ask and send me a message of the game your using, credit me somewhere in the video or description and a link to my channel please to show support.

Disclaimer note, this channel is not aimed at or made for children under the age of 13 , the video games I upload are for a general audience.

description: The Department of Fire Protection Engineering at the A. James Clark School of Engineering, University of Maryland was founded in 1956. To date we offer the only fully accredited undergraduate program and one of three graduate degree programs in the U.S. More than 1,100 graduates from the Department are now employed in industry, insurance companies, Federal, state or local government, military, and fire service. Our areas of research include suppression, flammability, flame spread, wildfires, detection, egress, fire modeling, fire dynamics, soot, turbulent combustion, and pyrolysis.

description:
TopPop was the first regular dedicated pop music TV show in the Dutch language area. Dutch broadcaster AVRO aired the programme weekly, from 1970 to 1988. 
Presenter Ad Visser hosted the show for its first fifteen years.
World famous music artists performed on TopPop: ABBA, 10CC, Bee Gees, The Jacksons, David Bowie, Earth & Fire, Boney M, Queen, Golden Earring, KC & The Sunshine Band, Chic and many more!

LICENSING
For licensing inquiries please contact toppop@avrotros.nl 

AVROTROS is a Dutch radio and television broadcaster, founded in 2014 from a merger of AVRO and TROS. From January 1st, 2014 the name of the merged broadcaster was used in joint programmes. AVRO was founded in 1923 as the Netherlands first public broadcaster. TROS started broadcasting in 1964. Toppop was a weekly AVRO pop program that was aired between 1970 and 1988.

HST is one of the oldest independent spindle repair facilities.
 
Each senior technician has over 15 years of experience.

Our database of over 100,000 spindle repairs proves our experience in virtually every type and model.

Our QTA program provides the fastest turnaround time for production critical spindles.

Our FEQA analyzes the cause of failure and provides recommendations to avoid future failures and improved spindle performance.

Modern equipment provides super precise balancing and analysis of your spindle.

Our warranty on repaired spindles meets or exceeds OEM warranties.

We only use ABEC 7 or better for all rolling element bearings.

All quotes are free of charge.

We're just the right size; big enough that we have a modern well equipped shop, and small enough that we know every customer and every customer is very important to us. And besides all of that, we are nice people to work with!

description: America is big with a wide variety of places ranging from beautiful to historical to whimsical. During my travels across America, I am going to take you to lots of these places. We'll visit everything from some of the best known spots to some places which aren't on many maps. There is a lot of variety in America. Hi, I'm Phil Konstantin. My background is just about as diverse as this country. I've helped to run the computers in Mission Control at NASA during the Moon landings. I've been a California Highway Patrol officer, an author of lots of magazine and newspaper article and a couple of books, a TV reporter, I'm even a member of the Cherokee Nation. and lots more. I hope to use some of my inside knowledge to help take you to some of the most interesting places & tell you interesting stories - Check "Playlists" for videos by category. "Raw Video" means video which has not been edited or altered in any way. Some of them have no sounds. In others, you can only hear my helicopter.

Agencia EFE: Más de 85 años informando al mundo en español

EFE es la primera agencia de noticias en castellano, con 85 años de trayectoria que avalan su imparcialidad, su potencia, su credibilidad y su inmediatez.

EFE es una empresa informativa multimedia con una red de periodistas mundial. Más de dos mil profesionales de 60 nacionalidades trabajan, 24 horas al día y siete días por semana, desde 180 ciudades de 110 países y con tres mesas de edición en Madrid, Bogotá y Bangkok (servicio multimedia en inglés), para ofrecer sus productos a clientes en los cinco continentes.

EFE distribuye 3 millones de noticias al año en los diferentes soportes informativos: texto, fotografía, audio, video y multimedia, que llegan diariamente a más de dos millares de medios de comunicación en el mundo, con una audiencia potencial de 250 millones de personas.

Suscríbete a nuestro canal para estar al día de toda la información nacional e internacional y los directos más destacados.

description:
rAVe [PUBS], founded in 1998 by Gary Kayye, is a news organization that provides coverage of the commercial (ProAV) and residential (HomeAV) audiovisual trade industries via e-newsletters, blogs, video, social media, and a variety of other mediums.

The target audience for rAVe's publications is what we call "AV Insiders" -- AV dealers, integrators, consultants, designers, etc. that deal in the sale, specification, design and installation of audiovisual products. We do not target what most people call "end users," though a small percentage of rAVe's readers may qualify as such, especially on the ProAV side of things.

The majority of what is provided on this YouTube channel are product pitches filmed at tradeshows from manufacturers and distributors in the AV Industry. These videos are meant to give you an idea about what the product is and why you might consider getting more information. Other videos include rAVe's creative promotional videos and web shorts.

description:
Podotherapie Hermanns is een groepspraktijk voor podotherapie met vestigingen in Limburg, Noord-Brabant, Gelderland, Zuid-Holland, Noord-Holland, Utrecht, Zeeland en in Overijssel. 

Ons ons team uit zo’n 80 medewerkers. Dit zijn (sport)-podotherapeuten, podotherapeuten met specialisatie in diabetes, zolentechnici en administratief personeel. Al onze podotherapeuten zijn aangesloten bij de NVvP (Nederlandse Vereniging van Podotherapeuten) en geregistreerd in het Kwaliteitsregister van Paramedici. Er wordt voortdurend geïnvesteerd in de nieuwste technieken en behandelmethodes (3D-scan, drukmeetplaat). En we werken intensief samen met andere disciplines (zoals fysiotherapeuten en manueel therapeuten enz.) zodat u altijd verzekerd bent van het juiste advies. Dit alles betaalt zich uit in een goede beleving van de zorg die wij leveren. Zo waarderen onze patiënten ons met een 8.8. Bovendien bestempelt 87% van de huisartsen de zorg van Podotherapie Hermanns minimaal met een ‘Goed’.

My youtube channel is a collection of RC and FPV related videos but also family/fun stuff, camera/tech bits and anything else that interests me.

I make youtube videos for fun and aim to make short useful videos where I feel I can do something a bit different, so I try to avoid common reviews unless I can do something different. 

Everything I review is bought with my own money as a normal customer (I am not a fan of paid reviews or reviewers), so I can give my open and honest opinion.

I pretty much delete any abusive/trolling comments, but try to respond to serious questions, but please read video descriptions first as I try to put details in there where possible, also please don't ask me for links as I don't recommend any particular vendor, and links are outdated within a day or two, so just search for best price in your country.

description:
An envisioning of the world's future transportation systems.
 
Webeo Transportation is located at the very interchange of my lifelong interests.
 
Since I was young, I always yearned to implement my track knot onto our world’s interchange web. Nevertheless, without the resources, nothing would be immediately possible. Rather than continue building on my room’s tangle, I decided to construct a new dimension to my littered atlases: on Google Earth.
 
Each video consists of a proposal, ranging from railways to roadways, each connecting to each other and to America’s fascinating transportation web. These videos are not merely my personal opinion, but act as a beacon for discussions, where others can discuss any possible improvements to my proposals.
 
My end goal, in addition to making my envisionings realities, is to transport people, improve economies, and make the world a better place for all and all to come.
 
REMEMBER: VIDEO + WEB = WEBEO

Päinvastoin, olen todella tyytyväinen siitä, että ihmiset voivat katsoa videoitani vapaasti ilman että minun pitää maksaa ylläpidosta yhtään mitään. En pidä pakkomainonnasta ja mielestäni ennen varsinaista ohjelmaa edeltävät kuluttajaa aliarvioivat rahastusyritykset ovat erittäin häiritseviä. Periaatetta voisi verrata siihen että ennen viinin maistelua nauttisi rasiallisen yskänpastilleja. Se vain laimentaa kokemusta ja laskee sen arvoa. Pahoittelut.

We know you're all fab, but here are some short house rules:

• Please be respectful of each other and of our record holders.
• We will always welcome new applications - if you think you can break a record, please do apply. 
• Spam posts will result in an instant ban.
• If you have a question about an application or a customer services issue you'd like to raise with the team, please head to www.guinnessworldrecords.com/contact to send a message.

description:
Videos from the Robot Locomotion Group at the MIT Computer Science and Artificial Intelligence Laboratory. 

The goal of our research is to build machines which exploit their natural dynamics to achieve extraordinary agility and efficiency. We believe that this challenge involves a tight coupling between mechanical design and underactuated nonlinear control, and that tools from machine learning and optimal control can be used to produce this coupling when classical control techniques fail. Our projects include minimally-actuated dynamic walking on moderate terrain, quadrupedal locomotion on extreme terrain, fixed-wing acrobatics, flapping-winged flight, and feedback control for fluid dynamics.

The Robot Locomotion Group is a part of the CSAIL Center for Robotics.

description:
SAMCAM GmbH is the number one company in Switzerland for aerial, mountain and street cinematography.

For over 10 years we've been among the leading production teams in the alps for aerial shooting. We've won many international awards for our images. We know our local mountains like the back of our hand. When everyone else is going home for the day, that's when the light gets good in the mountains, and then our work starts.

With our newest achievement – the Motocrane – which is exclusively used by us in Switzerland, fascinating and unique street shots are created. The air is our core competence – here we work with the Shotover, the Cineflex or with drones.

For us there's no such thing as good or bad weather. there's only interesting weather. we look around, focus on a particular detail and let it appear in all its grandeur.

channelName: For Amusement Only e.V. - Flipper- und Arcademuseum Seligenstadt
description:
Auf diesem Kanal werden Aufnahmen gezeigt, die im Flipper- und Arcademuseum in Seligenstadt entstanden.

Träger des Museums ist der Verein For Amusement Only e.V., welcher sich 2009 aus Sammlern und Bastlern von Arcade und Flippergeräten in Rodenbach gründete. Dort stand auch das erste Museum, welches aber nach einiger Zeit zu klein wurde.

Im hessischen Seligenstadt fand man 2013 ein neues Zuhause. Im jetzigen Gebäude finden nun ca. 250 Geräte bei rund 700m² auf zwei Etagen Platz. Gleichzeitig repariert und wartet man Geräte, hält diese für die Nachwelt spielbereit und archiviert Platinen sowie die Daten von Arcadegeräten. Auch das abfilmen der Geräte für diesen YouTube-Kanal gehört zum Nachhalten der Gamingkultur.

Das Museum hat jeden ersten Samstag im Monat von 12 - 21 Uhr geöffnet.
Für den Eintritt benötigt man ein Ticket, welches über die Webseite bezogen werden kann.

Flipper- und Arcademuseum Seligenstadt
Wilhelm-Leuschner-Str. 6, 63500 Seligenstadt
www.flipperundarcade.de

What can I say, I just love aviation and I guess this channel is a result of it.

Full HD trip reports is what this channel is all about, with the occasional spotting video thrown in. Being based in Singapore/Kochi, you'll see most of my trips originate from COK/SIN.

I usually try to upload a video every month, likely during the first week.

For editing, I've upgraded to Sony Movie Studio Platinum 12 Visual Effects 2. That's a mouthful isn't it?

I hope you enjoyed my music which I've been making on my own using FL studio 11 and a Casio keyboard.

description: The California High-Speed Rail Authority is responsible for planning, designing, building and operation of the first high-speed rail system in the nation. California high-speed rail will connect the mega-regions of the state, contribute to economic development and a cleaner environment, create jobs and preserve agricultural and protected lands. The system will run from San Francisco to the Los Angeles basin in under three hours at speeds capable of over 200 miles per hour. The system will eventually extend to Sacramento and San Diego, totaling 800 miles with up to 24 stations. In addition, the Authority is working with regional partners to implement a state-wide rail modernization plan that will invest billions of dollars in local and regional rail lines to meet the state's 21st century transportation needs.

description:
Hello my name is Oliver. The majority of my videos are at locations in the South East of England, but I do occasionally travel further afield. If you like what you see on my channel, then please like and subscribe, leave me a comment on any of my videos, or the discussion section on my channel, I do reply when I have the time, and stay tuned to further content! I use a Panasonic hc-V160 to film my videos/ iPhone 5SE.

Any station or track side location requests will be considered. Any queries or anything you would like to ask me about my channel, then please do leave a comment in my comments section. I hope you enjoy my content!

Thanks to everyone that has Subscribed to me so far!

description:
This YouTube channel belongs to Manorama Music – a popular music label based in Kochi, Kerala, India. We are the electronic media division of The Malayala Manorama Company Private Limited. Our specialization lies in producing and distributing music albums, movie soundtracks, devotional music, classical songs, and other forms of music content. We have an extensive collection of songs available in Malayalam and other regional languages of South India. Additionally, we are pioneers in creating animation content for kids. We offer channels in multiple languages such as Tamil, Telugu, Kannada, Hindi, Bengali, Marathi, Gujarati, and Punjabi.
We have a significant digital presence in the music streaming space through well-known platforms like iTunes, Amazon Music, Spotify, Gaana, JioSaavn, Wynk, and Hungama, to name a few.
Overall, Manorama Music is a recognized name in the Indian music industry and has played a vital role in promoting regional music culture.
